{"tid":2399050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"揭發　沙中線紅磡站工程剪短鋼筋　政府只票控禮頓200呎機房水泥","createTime":"2021-02-07T19:49:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T13:06:58.000Z","uid":261647,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e2df82df1ffb1d82f0cc3f7e15b3295951441f2f","tid":2399050,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T19:49:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/factwire/posts/1668011553405892\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffactwire%2Fposts%2F1668011553405892&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=ad4e4549\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/factwire/posts/1668011553405892</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cNhFgob.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcNhFgob.jpg&h=d0e5bcd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：FactWire News Agency 傳真社<br />\n<br />\n【沙中線】沙中線獨立調查委員會去年公布紅磡站擴建工程最終報告，直指工程造工差劣，港鐵和承建商禮頓須對管理和監察系統出現嚴重失誤負責。政府當時表示已向禮頓提出檢控，案件原本上月提堂，禮頓要求押後。<br />\n<br />\nFactWire傳真社查閱傳票，發現控罪原來只涉及一個約200呎製冷機房的鋼筋混凝土基腳工程，外界最關注涉剪短鋼筋的範圍、螺絲帽沒有妥善安裝等問題，都沒有包括在內。<br />\n<br />\n足本報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36MWOkI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36MWOkI&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=493f9f6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36MWOkI</a><br />\nEnglish version: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cQ69fs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cQ69fs&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUigmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=e413d044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cQ69fs</a>"},{"pid":"212429520db56611bc1773c1ae593afaa1c5ec96","tid":2399050,"uid":325200,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T23:56:10.000Z","msg":"開始跟大陸個套豆腐渣工程"},{"pid":"04050b95bc81c4a0ae8c169b2e144b7e455b7937","tid":2399050,"uid":57073,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T23:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a